data.description: Make yourself at home in this beautiful 3/2, split bedroom Tiber. This home backs to a fully mulched, landscaped backyard, an oasis with privacy, a lemon tree and avocado tree! Front, back and side landscaping newly manicured.All carpet and tile professionally cleaned and sanitized - 2024. New roof - 2023. AC replaced - 2023. Kitchen updated - 2022. Enjoy the 55+ Florida lifestyle with all that Ponte Vecchio has to offer! Newly renovated clubhouse - completion 2024! So many clubs and amenities to keep you busy. Your safety is a priority and PV boasts it's very own C.O.P. Patrol!Easy access to 95 and Turnpike. Close to shoppes, restaurants, entertainment and nature areas.Welcome home to your Piece of Paradise on Terni Lane in Ponte Vecchio
